				{
					"name": "Get Driver Detail",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/drivers/1/",
							"host": [
								"{{base_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"drivers",
								"1",
								""
							]
						},
						"description": "Get detailed information about a specific driver including full user profile and vehicle details."
					},
					"response": []
				}
			],
			"description": "Driver profile management, balance recharge, and driver listing endpoints."
		},
		{
			"name": "4. Ride Management",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Request Ride (Rider)",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.environment.set(\"ride_id\", jsonData.ride.id);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							},
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"driver_id\": 1,\n    \"price\": 50.00,\n    \"pickup_location\": \"123 Main St, City\",\n    \"dropoff_location\": \"456 Oak Ave, City\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/rides/request/",
							"host": [
								"{{base_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"rides",
								"request",
								""
							]
						},
						"description": "Rider requests a ride from an available driver. Sends real-time notification to driver via WebSocket."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Accept Ride (Driver)",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/rides/{{ride_id}}/accept/",
							"host": [
								"{{base_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"rides",
								"{{ride_id}}",
								"accept",
								""
							]
						},
						"description": "Driver accepts a pending ride request. Sets driver availability to false. Sends notification to rider."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Reject Ride with Counter Price (Driver)",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							},
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"rejection_price\": 75.00\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/rides/{{ride_id}}/reject/",
							"host": [
								"{{base_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"rides",
								"{{ride_id}}",
								"reject",
								""
							]
						},
						"description": "Driver rejects ride with a counter price offer. Sends notification to rider with new price."
					},
					"response": []
				},
				{
					"name": "Re-request Ride (Rider accepts counter price)",
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/rides/{{ride_id}}/rerequest/",
							"host": [
								"{{base_url}}"
							],
							"path": [
								"api",
								"rides",
								"{{ride_id}}",
								"rerequest",
								""
							]
						},
						"description": "Rider accepts driver's counter price and re-requests the ride. Changes status from rejected to pending with new price."
					},
					"response": []
				}
			],
			"description": "Ride request, acceptance, rejection, and counter-pricing endpoints."
		},
		{
			"name": "5. WebSocket Testing (HTML Pages)",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "WebSocket Test Instructions",
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [],
						"url": {
							"raw": "",
							"host": [
								""
							]
						},
						"description": "WebSocket endpoints cannot be tested directly in Postman. Use the HTML test pages provided in the WebSocket_Test_Pages folder.\n\n**WebSocket Endpoints:**\n\n1. **Ride Notifications:**\n   - URL: `ws://localhost:8000/ws/notifications/?token=YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN`\n   - Purpose: Real-time ride request/accept/reject notifications\n   - Available to: Both drivers and riders\n\n2. **Driver Location Tracking:**\n   - URL: `ws://localhost:8000/ws/location/?token=YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN`\n   - Purpose: Real-time driver location updates\n   - Drivers: Send location updates\n   - Riders: Receive location updates for tracked drivers\n\n**Message Formats:**\n\nDriver sends location:\n```json\n{\n    \"type\": \"location_update\",\n    \"latitude\": 40.7128,\n    \"longitude\": -74.0060\n}\n```\n\nRider receives location:\n```json\n{\n    \"type\": \"location_update\",\n    \"driver_id\": 1,\n    \"latitude\": \"40.712800\",\n    \"longitude\": \"-74.006000\",\n    \"timestamp\": \"2025-01-15T10:30:00Z\"\n}\n```\n\nRide notification:\n```json\n{\n    \"type\": \"ride_requested\",\n    \"message\": \"New ride request from Jane Rider\",\n    \"ride\": {\n        \"id\": 1,\n        \"status\": \"pending\",\n        \"price\": \"50.00\",\n        \"pickup_location\": \"123 Main St\",\n        \"dropoff_location\": \"456 Oak Ave\"\n    }\n}\n```"
					},
					"response": []
				}
			],
			"description": "WebSocket connection information and testing instructions."
		}
	],
